reviewText: I actually bought it and it's my favorite movie. Its way better than kung fu panda and I recommend to watch 'Golden Shoes'.Also the DVD burns well in fire after I watched it. Would recommend any family to watch it.

Horrible.
Trash animation, voice acting that is too fast to understand, and just a trash ripoff of Kung Fu Panda.

Don't even buy this trash movie, just buy Kung Fu Panda, it's SO MUCH BETTER THAN THIS TRASH.
I absolutely loved this movie. It is the best thing ever.

I am 20 minutes in and so far I've vomited in my mouth several times, laughed my ass off at the godawful animation, and facepalmed more times than I can count.

10/10

5 stars

better than Avatar...the last airbender movie...

I watched these on youtube and now I'm coming on Amazon to do a public service by warning parents not to waste thier money on this crap! Imagin a child asking for Kungfu Panda. Then thier parents see this in the store and buy it insteadXD Its just horrible! If you want your child to love you forever stay away from this!
The single best movie ever produced. Papa would be proud.

Vídeo Brinquedo USA has this on their YouTube, so don't bother buying it.
[...]

Another rip off by our friends from Video Brinquedo.
The animation is horrendous and the voice actors know it. Which explains the subpar acting.
The plot is loosely based on Kungfu Panda only nowhere near as creative.
I pity any child whose grandparents picked up this rubbish by mistake.
Watch it on youtube for free if you can't Video Brinquedo should not be rewarded for such a shameless rip-off of a superior film.
Still better than The Amazing Bulk.
One of Video Brinquedo's  greatest master pieces.

This movie is ugly. Even the cover looks bad. That pig thing in the background is just creepy...  Also the panda has square eyes. I wonder if it was animated by a seven year old.

P.S no offense to you seven year olds. You could probably do better animation than this junk.
Better than Kung-fu Panda 10/10 would watch again
